11. The personal mobility according to claim 1 further comprising:
a board;
at least one wheel provided on the board and rotated by a motor;
a brake indicator lamp provided on a rear side of the board, a left direction indicator lamp provided on a left side of the board, a right direction indicator lamp provided on a right side of the rear side of the board, and a warning indicator lamp provided on a bottom surface of the board.
